    "image_with_text_yKLHHB": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_EDDn49": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Tocotrienols Vitamin E",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_JJWpy3": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Tocotrienols are the most potent form of vitamin E, offering antioxidant protection that is 60 times more effective than alpha-tocopherol. Unlike conventional vitamin E supplements, which contain tocopherols that may interfere with tocotrienols' benefits, this formula is 100% derived from annatto and free of tocopherols. Backed by decades of research from Dr. Barrie Tan, the superior benefits of tocotrienols have been extensively studied for their impact on cellular health, cardiovascular function, bone strength, and brain support. </p><ul><li>Powerful cellular antioxidant protection</li><li>Cardiovascular health support</li><li>Brain and cognitive function</li><li>Bone density and metabolic health</li><li>Supports healthy ageing at a cellular level</li><li>100% annatto-derived, free of tocopherol interference</li></ul>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
        "button_RCr9ED": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
            "button_label": "Shop Now",
            "button_link": "shopify://products/tocotrienols-vitamin-e",
            "button_style_secondary": false
          }
        }
      },
