    "image_with_text_EapeUP": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_cpFMj7": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Think You’re Getting Enough Vitamin E?",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_QNdBXj": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Most people associate vitamin E with tocopherols, the more common form found in foods and multivitamins, but have you heard of tocotrienols? A more potent and bioavailable form of vitamin E with distinct health benefits, especially for cardiovascular, brain, and metabolic health.<br/><br/>Tocotrienols are significantly more potent antioxidants than tocopherols, helping to protect cells more effectively. However, studies suggest that too much tocopherol may reduce the benefits of tocotrienols, which is why a tocotrienol-only supplement is ideal. DeltaGold® tocotrienols come from the Annatto plant, the purest known source with no tocopherol interference.<br/><br/>Backed by research for many decades, and DeltaGold® tocotrienols is proven to deliver benefits for heart health, bone strength, brain function, and metabolic support.<br/><br/></p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
